## Interface: 120007
## Title: |cff00c7ffVRT|r |cffff8040Reader|r (Sessions)
## Notes: Required companion to VoidRaidTools. Captures boss cast events + friendly auras during raid encounters and uploads (with your consent) to api.voidscout.io. First-run dialog explains exactly what's collected; /vrtr optout to keep recordings local-only. Discord: https://discord.gg/7ZHmx7zMDh
